ModelResponse(parts=[ToolCallPart(tool_name='final_result', args='{""sparql_query"": ""PREFIX brick: <https://brickschema.org/schema/1.1/Brick#>\\nPREFIX s223: <http://example.org/s223#>\\nPREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>\\nPREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>\\n\\nSELECT DISTINCT ?zone ?zoneLabel WHERE {\\n  # Entity must be a Zone\\n  ?zone a brick:Zone .\\n  OPTIONAL { ?zone rdfs:label ?zoneLabel . }\\n  \\n  {\\n    # Directly associated Property (any predicate linking the zone to a Property)\\n    ?zone ?anyPredicate ?property .\\n    ?property a brick:Property .\\n  }\\n  UNION\\n  {\\n    # Indirect connection via a RoomDomainSpace (any length path of connections)\\n    ?zone (rdf:* ) ?room .\\n    ?room a s223:RoomDomainSpace .\\n    ?room (rdf:* ) ?property .\\n    ?property a brick:Property .\\n  }\\n}""}', tool_call_id='chatcmpl-tool-ef81cfb50a57456ea7e201124572b3a0', part_kind='tool-call')], model_name='hosted_vllm/hosted_vllm/gpt-oss-120b', timestamp=datetime.datetime(2026, 1, 21, 18, 57, 59, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), kind='response')
